latestPosts.caption:
To My Love, On Your Birthday

Whether it’s one year or fifty we share, 
You’re my first, my last—forever there. 
Every meal, every story I tell, 
In your love, I’ve always dwelled so well.

My expressions, my moods, even my cries, 
My gossips, my laughs, my lows and highs. 
Food we savor, long drives we take
We share thoughts, we trade our views, 
Grow together, in love we choose. 
Helping each other, side by side, 
In this bond, we take such pride.

Thanks for walking into my Life 
You’re the man I adore. 
A wonderful soul 
Happy birthday, my love❤️🧿
